quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,"Toto efwe khwakhwikulila obushili bwa habulafu."
  48,2,"Kho Nyasaye akhuleshele ebionoono bibio biaranjilila nende biamalilikha, ne akhwitsusilie emikabo chichie, ne akhulunjisie khunjila ingololofu."
  48,3,"Ne akhuhabine obuhabini bwa amaani."
  48,4,"Niye weshia obuyeenzefu mumioyo chia abasuubili; kho anyoole okhubameeta obusuubili hekulu wobusuubili bwabu. Ne omukaanda kwabalwani beliyie kwomwikulu nende kwokhushialo ni kwa Nyasaye, ne Nyasaye niye Omumanyi po, Owamachesi muno."
  48,5,"Kho yenjisie Abasuubili abasatsa naabakhasi mumikunda chiomwikulu chiburangamwo emialo, balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, mana abaleshele tsimbi tsiabu, ne okho imbeli wa Nyasaye nikho okhubura okhukhongo."
  48,6,"Ne abahelesie eshinyasio abeshikhabili abasatsa naabakhasi, nende abatsokaasinjia Nyasaye abasatsa nabakhasi, abapariranga Nyasaye amaparo amabii. Kuliboolela omukalukhano omubii, ne Nyasaye yabasinyishila, mana nabatsuba, ne nabarecheshela omulilo kwa Jahannam, ne ni amakalushilo amabii muno."
  48,7,"Ne abalwani beliyie bo mwikulu nende bomushialo ni ba Nyasaye, ne Nyasaye ni wa amaani, Owamachesi muno."
  48,8,"Toto efwe khwakhuruma obe Omuloli, Omuboli wa amakhuwa koomwikhoyo, Omwikanyilisi."
  48,9,"Kho musuubile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, ne mumukhoonye, ne mumuwe eshiribwa, ne mwitsomie Nyasaye itsuli nende ingolobe."